metadata.name: Photography Is Forever
metadata.description:
The world is quiet and still,  
As the year comes to an end.  
The streets are empty and dark,  
As the hour grows late.  
But in this moment of solitude,  
I find a sense of peace.

The worries and fears of the past,  
Fade away in the night.  
And I am left with only myself,  
And the memories of the year.

I reflect on the joys and sorrows,  
The highs and the lows.  
And I am grateful for the journey,  
For all that it has shown.

So I take a deep breath,  
And let go of the past.  
Embracing the present,  
And all that it holds.

As the new year approaches,  
I stand ready and strong,  
To embrace the future,  
And all that it brings.
